        					<h3>Iron Man</h3>
        					<p>Tony Stark is a genius, billionaire, philanthropist, and a founding member of the Avengers. A brilliant inventor, he designed the revolutionary high-tech exoskeleton powered by the Arc Reactor in his chest, becoming the armored superhero known as Iron Man.</p>
