        				<div class="avenge">
        					<h3>Hulk</h3>
        					<p>Doctor Robert Bruce Banner, M.D., Ph.D., is a renowned scientist and a founding member of the Avengers. Highly respected for his work in biochemistry, nuclear physics, and gamma radiation, he was commissioned by Thaddeus Ross to recreate the Super Soldier Serum which created Captain America, although Ross elected not to inform Banner what he was creating.</p>
        					<a class="button" href="captain.html">Read Profile</a>
        					
        				</div>
        			</div>
        			<div class="container">
        				<img class="image" src="hawkeye.png">
        				<div class="avenge">
        					<h3>Hawkeye</h3>
        					<p>Clinton Francis "Clint" Barton, also known as Hawkeye, is a skilled marksman, a former special agent of S.H.I.E.L.D. and one of the founding members of the Avengers. Known for his use of the bow and arrow as his primary weapon, Barton had become one of the best agents of S.H.I.E.L.D., responsible for the recruitment of Black Widow, whom he developed a strong friendship with. Assigned by Nick Fury into watching over the Tesseract, he was brainwashed by Loki and used as his pawn for all his evil schemes. </p>
